2008-06-27  Richard Frith-Macdonald <rfm@gnu.org>

	* Source/NSPropertyList.m: sort dictionary keys only if they are
	strings.  This is the new MacOS-X behavior (old behavior was to sort
	if all responded to compare:).
	Fixes bug #23727

