	* Source/NSPropertyList.m: Corrected setup so that compilation 
	works on Solaris 9.  

2005-05-08  Richard Frith-Macdonald <rfm@gnu.org>

	* Source/NSString.m: nul terminate properly when a returned 'C string'
	is actually unicode.
